{"tid":1053329,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"英超調查曼城涉違FFP","createTime":"2019-03-09T03:22:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T04:01:24.000Z","uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"4ec74e9359803cdbc4c237380ac628941c2402e3","tid":1053329,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T03:22:07.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=i2Kzi6k%2Bo1XjTd2IKJX6uTbcp9x5SJfJ3tUQBIbvNjo%3D&h=3e176a08\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】英超賽會周五證實，將會調查曼城涉嫌違反財政公平條例一事。<br />\n<br />\n德國《明鏡周刊》早前報道，指獲得流出文件證實曼城違反財政公平條例，當中包括早年非法付出了20萬鎊，以簽入只得14歲的翼鋒查頓辛祖；歐洲足協於周四證實，旗下獨立調查委員會將展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n事件觸動了英超賽會的神經，決定同樣立案調查曼城，更指將會集中調查這支英超榜首球隊的財政狀況，以及年輕球員的轉會。<br />\n<br />\n藍月已經否認一切，至於領隊哥迪奧拿（Pep Guardiola）在周五賽前記者會亦表示，這些指控不會令他於球隊的功績蒙上污點：「球會已發出聲明，我不能夠補充更多。這家球會很透明，希望事件盡快完結。」<br />\n<br />\n圖片來源 : &copy;AFP"},{"pid":"b3657adc777f35fbe32d8fe19375e11f22f743d3","tid":1053329,"uid":70754,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T03:23:56.000Z","msg":"-3分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"a4c0f428b1746b1462f203f05c55641110dae70f","tid":1053329,"uid":48222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T03:25:10.000Z","msg":"一定冇事啦<br />\n嘥鳩氣"},{"pid":"a01fc9489dcfb937e03b51fe81265e1d80ae1e1d","tid":1053329,"uid":760,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T03:25:51.000Z","msg":"禁冇得踢歐聯就夠"},{"pid":"a12a711da81f58c6b8c54d56eea2eab1d0d52b1a","tid":1053329,"uid":36811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T03:26:54.000Z","msg":"巴黎都未有事 鏝點會有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81112fc1ee9324863d5eccd44727572728c56c98","tid":1053329,"uid":75479,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-09T03:28:53.000Z","msg":"鏝聯賽扣分，猁奪冠劇本 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{